#TTRPG BOT

# TTRPG BOT

## Description
A discord bot for TTRPG players that like to play TTRPG games online, this is an inventory management bot. The DM has admin access to add or remove from players inv, players have their own permissions to only view their own inventory. When you react, a modal opens with inventory icons and when clicked another modal opens with item information.

